<center>
<body>
<% if @result == "Player 1 Wins" %>
<h1><%= @player_1.name %>, you chose <%= @player_1_move.move %> and CPU chose <%= @cpu_move.move%>.</h1>
Therefore, you Win! <%= @player_1_move.move %> beats <%= @cpu_move.move%>
<% elsif @result == "Player 2 Wins"%>
<h1><%= @player_1.name %>, you chose <%= @player_1_move.move %> and CPU chose <%= @cpu_move.move%>. </h1> 
Therefore, you Lose! <%= @cpu_move.move %> beats <%= @player_1_move.move %>
<% else %>
<h1><%= @player_1.name %>, you chose <%= @player_1_move.move %> and CPU chose <%= @cpu_move.move%>.</h1> 
Therefore, it's a Draw! <%= @player_1_move.move %> and <%= @cpu_move.move %> cancel eachother out!
<% end %>
Would you like to play again?
<form action="/play-again" method="post">
  <input type="submit" value="Yes" name="playagain">
</form>
<form action="/final-score" method="post">
  <input type="submit" value="No" name="playagain">
</form>
</body>
</center>